{'time': '2023-02-24T99:00:00-04:00', 'text': 'Posted a couple dozen articles translated into English fromthe 1959 and 1960 issues of _H ongqi_ [ _Red Flag_ ], the theoretical journalof the Communist Party of China beginning in 1958.  [**China/Magazines/Hongqi Page**](https://www.bannedthought.net/China/Magazines/Hongqi/index.htm)', 'source': 'https://www.bannedthought.net/RecentPostings.htm'}